{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If not found, optionally searches by filename anywhere under the project dir\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Replaces take source with the found original file (no new PCM file created)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Removes trailing "\u55357 ?\u56637 ?" from take name\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Strips the RA_OFP: line from notes\sa180\par}
